# UI Components Guidelines

## Component Design Principles
- Single Responsibility: Mỗi component chỉ làm một việc
- Composition over Inheritance
- Props interface rõ ràng và intuitive
- Consistent API design across components

## Styling System

### Tailwind CSS
- Ưu tiên sử dụng Tailwind utility classes
- Custom utilities cho patterns lặp lại
- Responsive design với mobile-first approach
- Dark mode support với dark: variants

### Component Structure
```tsx
interface ButtonProps {
  variant?: 'primary' | 'secondary' | 'danger';
  size?: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg';
  disabled?: boolean;
  loading?: boolean;
  children: React.ReactNode;
  onClick?: () => void;
}

export const Button: React.FC<ButtonProps> = ({
  variant = 'primary',
  size = 'md',
  disabled = false,
  loading = false,
  children,
  onClick,
  ...props
}) => {
  // Component implementation
};
```

## State Management
- Local state với useState/useReducer
- Global state với Zustand
- Server state với TanStack Query
- Form state với controlled components

## Accessibility (A11y)
- Semantic HTML elements
- ARIA attributes khi cần
- Keyboard navigation support
- Screen reader friendly
- Focus management
- Color contrast compliance

## Performance Optimization
- React.memo cho components expensive
- useMemo cho calculations
- useCallback cho event handlers
- Lazy loading cho components lớn
- Image optimization

## Common UI Patterns

### Layout Components
- Container - Max width và centering
- Grid - Flexible grid system
- Stack - Vertical/horizontal spacing
- Flex - Flexbox utilities

### Interactive Components
- Button - All variants và states
- Input - Form inputs với validation
- Modal - Overlay với backdrop
- Dropdown - Select và menu patterns

### Feedback Components
- Toast - Success/error notifications
- Loading - Spinner và skeleton screens
- Empty State - No data scenarios
- Error Boundary - Error handling UI

## Component Testing
- Render testing với React Testing Library
- User interaction testing
- Accessibility testing
- Visual regression testing với Storybook
- Props validation testing

## Documentation
- JSDoc comments cho props
- Storybook stories cho showcase
- Usage examples trong README
- API documentation

## Design Tokens
- Colors: Primary, secondary, neutral palettes
- Typography: Font sizes, weights, line heights
- Spacing: Consistent spacing scale
- Shadows: Elevation system
- Border radius: Consistent rounding
- Breakpoints: Responsive design points
